I bet you're wondering what just happened. Well, basically, Sam, Destiel shipper he is, saw a chance. And he took it.
Sam walked a few feet toward Dean and Cas. He pushed Dean into Cas. They made out for a while.
"Hey guys, I'm going to the store, have sex while I'm gone!" he yelled to them, walking out the door again.
Dean never complained about going to the dentist again.